
  LOGIC OF MY CODE :
  I am declare two variables left and right that contains the sum of diagonal elements and using only one for loop i achieved my output in time of O(n).

   int left=0;
   int right=0;
  int (i=0 ; i<n; i++){
   left+=arr[i][i];
   right+=arr[i][n-1-i];
}
  return Math.abs(right-left);




  
